<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stable-adj">stable <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'steɪbl/    美 /'steɪbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-steady">1.★ <strong>稳定的；牢固的 (steady)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a stable job
稳定的工作</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>沉稳的；稳重的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s about the most stable person I know.
我认识的人当中，大概数他最稳重。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Water can absorb and give off a lot of heat without big changes in temperature, thus creating a <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (稳定的) environment.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. stable  </p></div>